Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭帶八一行乘坐月精靈號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往月球時的殘骸課裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,課長 這張照片是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.31,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是相親照片 給小八的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個美人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給頭帶八太浪費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過離過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.82,0:00:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,課長 介紹給我不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同病相憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過女方據說是個日本迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小八的情況後很積極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本？ 日本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.90,0:00:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭帶八和田名部都算不上什麼日本人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會忍術和空手道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.47,0:00:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次想請田名部在宴會上表演轉圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.31,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉圈是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是拉腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.55,0:01:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 殿下大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？ 小愛不會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.76,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是日本人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 難得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人不會做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是日本古裝劇裡才會有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古裝劇是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國的話就是西部片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像不會真有槍手開槍後往槍口吹氣一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是故事片中才會有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那忍者也沒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是啊喳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍者和武士是200多年以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.59,0:01:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊喳不是日本是中國的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小尤對日本很了解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤利君 你會說日語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.57,0:01:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次和小八說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以前有點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小尤真多才多藝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來還有一個相親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.95,0:02:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方希望找俄羅斯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.12,0:02:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球上有人留守嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢？ 課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤利君在站上已經整整七年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒有交往的人 不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡相親吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過命運的邂逅也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭訕也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相親也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是一種相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的不是相遇的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是和誰相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我也是相親的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.62,0:02:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 結婚暫時沒有考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時是多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 雖然我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也許殘骸知道
